  "title": "Link to the searching guides on the specific widgets/connectors doc",
  "body": "I had a live-chat today, where the user had an issue with the pagination because it did not calculate the correct number of pages.\r\n\r\nIn the end, it was a limitation from Algolia API documented here (https://www.algolia.com/doc/guides/searching/pagination/#pagination-limitations) in which its automatically limit the max nbPages to 34.\r\n\r\nThe user suggested to link this kind of searching guides to the connectors/widgets pages to learn more on how it works behind and avoid this kind of frustration thinking that Algolia is broken.\r\n\r\nWhat do you think @Haroenv @bobylito ?",
